data.description: Spacious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath in a quiet area of Pike County near the Bogue Chitto River.  This home features a spacious, well equipped kitchen perfect for entertaining large groups of family and friends. The large living room is equipped with a gas log fireplace and beautiful natural-wood crown molding, making it a cozy and inviting space for you and your family.  The exterior of this house features brick walls and a metal roof as well as a whole-home generator making it safe and sound from the elements.  Off the carport there is shop/man cave that features built in shelving as well as a garage door.  On the other side of the carport is a a fully equipped outdoor kitchen area perfect for grilling come football season.  The large, covered front porch is perfect for relaxing in the quiet peacefulness of the surrounding country side.  Make your appointment to come see this perfect family home today.
